# Terraform working files (every env)
terraform/**/.terraform/
terraform/**/*.tfvars
!terraform/**/*.tfvars.example
# Scratch validate-only tfvars under test/ are committed (no secrets, fake values for `terraform validate`).
!terraform/**/test/*.tfvars
terraform/**/*.tfstate
terraform/**/*.tfstate.backup
terraform/**/crash.log
# Note: .terraform.lock.hcl IS committed (Terraform best practice — pins provider versions).
